Name: Combo Assault (Blast)
Desc:
[Enchant Force]
Attacks nearby enemies with a bow, and then shoots arrows flying through space to attack a wide range of enemies.
Deals a more powerful blow by empowering the bow.

H.Old:
Relic Gauge Cost: 100. Bow attack deals damage to up to 1 enemies at 600% damage 8 times. Damaged enemies are inflicted with 1 stacks of the Ancient Curse Debuff.
Arrows deal damage up to 10 enemies at 600% damage 5 times.
Cooldown: 20 sec.
